            </picture>
            <figcaption>
              {{ content.talksImageCaption }}:
              <a href="https://blog.nevercodealone.de/php-testing-refactoring-nca-conference-duisburg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                {{ content.talksImageLinkText }}
              </a>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <br class="only-print">

          <section class="avoid-page-break">
            <h3>Memberships, Events and Talks</h3>
            <p>
              From 2019 to 2021 I co-hosted the Cologne Web Performance meetup. Currentyl, I am a member of <a href="https://impact-hub-berlin.notion.site/Ingo-Steinke-2dd84e135fff4973ad8f06ddf9553890" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Impact Hub Berlin</a> and <a href="https://fairantwortung.org/uber-ingo-steinke/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fairantwortung</a>. I actively participate in professional discussions and write
              <a href="https://dev.to/ingosteinke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">blog posts</a> about technological topics.
            </p>
            <p>
              {{ content.talks2 }}
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.meetup.com/cologne-germany-high-performance-website-optimization-group/events/274558354/"
                  hreflang="de"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  {{ content.talkMeetupWebVitals }}
                </a>
                {{ content.talkMeetupWebVitals2 }}
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.meetup.com/cologne-germany-high-performance-website-optimization-group/events/268706480/"
                  hreflang="de"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  {{ content.talkPerformanceNoCode }}
                </a> {{ content.talkPerformanceNoCode2 }}
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.meetup.com/cologne-germany-high-performance-website-optimization-group/events/255856182/"
                  hreflang="de"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  {{ content.talkHsts }}
                </a>
                {{ content.talkHsts2 }}
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.meetup.com/cologne-germany-high-performance-website-optimization-group/events/zdnjlmywhbgb/"
                  hreflang="de"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  {{ content.talkInfrastructure }}
                </a>
                {{ content.talkInfrastructure2 }}
              </li>
            </ul>
            </p>
            <p>
              Creativity, flexibility, and thoughtfulness are values that guide my work and personal life. I am deeply interested in how sustainability, culture, and art come together, and I strive to bring what I learn into my work every day.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="avoid-page-break">
            <h4>{{ content.aboutMeEthicalHeading }}</h4>
            <p>
              Digitalisation primarily stands for technological progress. The economic benefits of sustainable innovation have often been overlooked. I like to to support ethical and ecological projects, for example the transition in the transport sector, renewable energies, and environmentally-friendly fashion. Thanks to my experience, we can elegantly comply with legal requirements such as the General Data Protection Regulation or the European Accessibility Act.
            </p>
          </section>

        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="tiled-content target-offset" id="projects">
        <div class="pl1">
          <h2>{{ content.projectsHeading }}</h2>
          <p>
            {{ content.projects }}
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-container grid-container--projects">
          {% include './_includes/projects.liquid', showallprojects: 'showallprojects', showicons: 'showicons'  %}
        </div>
      </section>

      <br>
      <span id="skills"></span>
      {% include './_includes/skills.liquid', showallskills: 'showallskills', skillsTitle: 'Professional Skills'  %}

